w":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女僕１","body":"客人，不好意思，在各位開心的時候打擾。這是下一個課題。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"走廊有很多扇門並列……\n會是怎樣的課題呢？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event97-06-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女僕２","body":"在此的其中一扇門後是能通往派對會場的書房。\n請猜中那一扇門。\n這就是這次的課題。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"亞子","body":"什麼嘛～！那很簡單啊！\n反正只要去選就好了吧！？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":24,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event97-06-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"女僕１","body":"但機會只有兩次。\n兩次當中沒有猜中的話，這個課題就算是失敗。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"咦？只有兩次！？\n這樣放眼看去，門大概有２０個左右耶？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":24,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event97-06-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"哇啊～雖然很嚴苛……但規則就是規則嘛。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf_left01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event97-06-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"亞子……這裡就交給你選了。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event97-06-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"亞子","body":"咦！？要亞子選嗎！？\n為、為什麼是亞子呢！？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event97-06-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"你在開始接觸樂團時，在展演會場裡\n眾多的樂團當中，\n選擇了Roselia。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event97-06-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"你的眼光沒有錯……如果是你，\n一定能做出正確的選擇……難道不是嗎?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event97-06-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"亞子","body":"友、友希那學姊……！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event97-06-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"的確……\n我也贊成友希那的意見。\n亞子，拜託你了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf_right01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":23,"motionNa